Dataset Description:
The dataset consists of 901 images belonging to two classes:
- With Mask: 494 images
- Without Mask: 407 images

The dataset was split into training and validation sets:
- Training images: 722
- Validation images: 179

Images were resized and normalized before training. Data generators were used for efficient loading and preprocessing.

The dataset contains images collected from multiple sources and includes varied lighting, orientations, and real-world scenarios for better generalization.

Google Drive Link:
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1uXFfS9CZaRCdNNxSaqpPqArQb-VDaZ5_?usp=sharing

Note:
The dataset is hosted on Google Drive due to its large size and is used strictly for academic purposes.

